another seat on the board.

07:16.160 --> 07:18.094
Oh, that shouldn't
be a problem.
And one more thing.

07:18.130 --> 07:19.893
No more drama.

07:19.940 --> 07:22.158
That's why Drescher
convinced them to peel away.

07:22.200 --> 07:23.758
Sweeney is too high maintenance.

07:23.810 --> 07:25.835
You're asking me
to guarantee no more drama

07:25.870 --> 07:27.098
from Mr. Sweeney?

07:27.140 --> 07:30.075
Can you guarantee he won't kill
anyone in the next five minutes?

07:30.110 --> 07:32.510
Well, I think that
shouldn't be a problem.

07:32.550 --> 07:34.848
Okay, well, Tenley will call in
his vote, and he's in our camp.

07:34.880 --> 07:35.972
How's Sweeney doing?

07:36.020 --> 07:39.012
SWEENEY:
First of all,
thank you for that question.

07:39.050 --> 07:42.156
Or should I thank your boss,
Mr. Drescher,

07:42.190 --> 07:44.556
for the question
he asked you to ask?
He's very good at this.

07:44.590 --> 07:46.182
IfI had stock,
I might even vote for him.

07:46.230 --> 07:48.095
Good. And good job, Alicia.

07:48.130 --> 07:49.563
I know how hard this Sweeney
business is on you.

07:49.600 --> 07:52.797
Oh, I'm fine.
But thank you.

07:52.840 --> 07:54.990
In fact, Diane, um,

07:55.040 --> 07:57.907
