08:05.850 --> 08:07.112
Let's just get Sweeney in
as CEO,

08:07.150 --> 08:08.117
and then we can talk about
a raise.

08:08.150 --> 08:09.845
Okay?
Okay. Thanks Diane.

08:09.890 --> 08:11.585
Hi, I'm Isobel Swift.

08:11.620 --> 08:16.011
_I work here as a contractor
in executive event planning.

08:16.060 --> 08:17.652
