08:19.960 --> 08:21.097
Who are you?

08:21.130 --> 08:22.995
Uh-oh.
Uh-oh? Why uh-oh?

08:23.030 --> 08:24.065
Drama.

08:24.100 --> 08:26.125
The woman you sexually harassed
when you hired me,

08:26.170 --> 08:29.936
