to sue you

08:32.810 --> 08:34.232
and Herald Equity
for sexual harassment.

08:34.280 --> 08:35.975
SWEENEY:
Young woman,

08:36.010 --> 08:37.773
you know for a fact
that's not true.

08:37.810 --> 08:40.574
