explain this?

08:42.720 --> 08:46.178
Meet your son, Mr. Sweeney.

09:01.600 --> 09:02.669
PEDRONO: The ninth floor,
north-facing.

09:02.710 --> 09:05.167
That's some of our best views.

09:05.210 --> 09:06.632
I understand, Mr. Pedrono.
How much are we talking?

09:06.680 --> 09:07.806
For your four bedroom?

09:07.840 --> 09:09.102
It's three bedroom and a bonus.

09:09.140 --> 09:11.847
Your three-and-a-half bedroom,
it's $1.2 million.

09:11.880 --> 09:14.610
But remember,
you can get great financing.

09:14.650 --> 09:16.618
And that's everything in?
What do you mean?

09:16.650 --> 09:18.618
I mean, I know when these
tenant-conversions go condo,

09:18.650 --> 09:19.981
they sometimes have add-ons.

09:20.020 --> 09:21.851
Well, you'll have to purchase
the parking space.

09:21.890 --> 09:23.926
And there will be a monthly
charge for the association fees.

09:23.960 --> 09:25.029
And that'll run me...?

09:25.060 --> 09:26.652
$35,000 for the parking,

09:26.700 --> 09:28.224
and 2,000 a month
for the association.

09:28.260 --> 09:30.728
Thank you. I'll get back to you.
CAITLIN: We lost the proxy vote,

09:30.770 --> 09:32.829
but we've applied for an
immediate injunction

09:32.870 --> 09:34.861
against the vote results.
Unfortunately...

09:34.900 --> 09:36.663
DIANE: There seems to be a
narrative of unfortunately's.

09:36.710 --> 09:39.736
CAITLIN: Yes. Unfortunately,
we are up against a deadline.

09:39.780 --> 09:41.600
Mr. Sweeney lost
the proxy fight,

09:41.640 --> 09:43.949
so, the law requires
he liquidate

09:43.980 --> 09:45.675
his shares in 72 hours.

09:45.710 --> 09:48.315
So we have _72 hours
to Win an injunction?
Yes.

09:48.350 --> 09:50.989
