two things in court.

09:51.020 --> 09:52.954
One, Isobel Swift's
accusations are a lie.

09:52.990 --> 09:54.309
That the paternity
is a lie?

09:54.360 --> 09:56.954
DAVID: No, the sexual
harassment is a lie.

09:56.990 --> 09:59.891
And the only proof of harassment
is paternity, so I'm applying

09:59.930 --> 10:01.989
for an immediate paternity test.
Go ahead, Caitlin.

10:02.030 --> 10:04.863
And second, we have
to prove this accusation

10:04.900 --> 10:06.959
was intended to throw
the proxy vote.

10:07.000 --> 10:09.332
If Drescher is
behind Isobel's lies,

10:11.370 --> 10:12.928
and Drescher will be
precluded from running.

10:12.980 --> 10:13.901
DIANE: So you need
to prove a connection

10:13.940 --> 10:16.647
between Isobel and Drescher?

10:16.680 --> 10:18.898
Yes. I am going to court today.

10:18.950 --> 10:21.839
