with Will and what cannot.

10:37.470 --> 10:39.688
So what does Mr. Sweeney
say about this woman?

10:39.740 --> 10:40.889
Um...

10:42.970 --> 10:45.336
He didn't touch her.
He hired her. But that's all.

10:45.370 --> 10:48.828
And we_ believe him?
Well, the timing of Isobel's
accusations seem suspicious.

10:48.880 --> 10:50.438
So, guardedly, yes.

10:50.480 --> 10:52.675
Good, so let's get moving.

10:57.120 --> 10:59.111
Thank you.

11:02.090 --> 11:03.057
You're on it, right?

11:03.090 --> 11:05.251
Finding a connection
between Drescher and Isobel?

11:05.290 --> 11:06.257
Yep.

11:06.290 --> 11:07.951
Alicia.
Yeah?

11:08.000 --> 11:08.955
Watch out

11:09.930 --> 11:11.363
I know, but I'm tired
of being paranoid.

11:11.400 --> 11:12.367
She's just hungry.

11:12.400 --> 11:13.992
Like a piranha.

11:14.040 --> 11:16.031
She's hiding
something.

11:18.140 --> 11:19.971
_ It's not about
havmg sex on my couch.

11:20.010 --> 11:22.308
(scattered chuckling)

11:22.340 --> 11:24.342
