38:50.060 --> 38:51.379
(groans)

38:51.430 --> 38:52.954
Notgood.

38:54.760 --> 38:57.399
I want to be clear that we did
not have sex in your office.

38:57.430 --> 38:59.489
Well, I'm relieved
to hear that.

39:01.770 --> 39:03.931
Bottom line, I thought
it was wrong for me to be

39:03.970 --> 39:06.063
pointing fingers if I wasn't
going to point one at myself.

39:06.110 --> 39:09.671
Well, I appreciate
your coming forward.

39:09.710 --> 39:11.541
It's brave.

39:11.580 --> 39:13.605
And it shows character.

39:13.650 --> 39:15.117
Thank you.

39:15.150 --> 39:16.811
So let's just
leave it at that.

39:20.450 --> 39:22.816
At...?

39:22.860 --> 39:25.420
What-whatwhat do you mean?

39:25.460 --> 39:27.678
Cary, I don't condone
what you did,

39:27.730 --> 39:29.789
but I know you.

39:29.830 --> 39:33.766
And I know your heart
is in the right place.

39:33.800 --> 39:36.496
So.... let'sjust
leave it at that.

39:36.540 --> 39:38.064
I'm sorry,

39:38.100 --> 39:40.000
sir, you said the rules have
to apply to everybody.

39:40.040 --> 39:41.166
They do.

39:41.210 --> 39:42.632
But not to me?

39:43.640 --> 39:45.471
Does anyone else know
about you and Dana?

39:45.510 --> 39:46.772
Yeah.

39:46.810 --> 39:48.812
(exasperated sigh)

39:51.220 --> 39:52.448
I think I need to resign.

39:52.490 --> 39:54.458
Absolutely not.

39:54.490 --> 39:57.755
Then I think I need to be placed
on temporary leave.

39:57.790 --> 39:59.849
There has to be
some consequence,

39:59.890 --> 40:02.199
or I'm going to lose respect
around here,

40:02.230 --> 40:03.527
and so are you.

40:04.570 --> 40:06.526
(sighs)

40:06.570 --> 40:09.835
Let me...

40:09.870 --> 40:12.737
Let me think about it, okay?

40:14.480 --> 40:16.698
Thank you.

40:18.610 --> 40:19.804
(door opens)

40:21.550 --> 40:24.212
ALICIA:
I don't think
there's much to get.

40:24.250 --> 40:25.319
She's not very conflicted.

40:25.350 --> 40:27.784
I'm not sure the glass ceiling
was broken for this.

40:27.820 --> 40:29.788
Actually, it probably was.

40:31.190 --> 40:33.829
She'll be back
in 15 years.

40:33.860 --> 40:34.997
Like you.

40:35.030 --> 40:37.157
No, I don't think so.

40:37.200 --> 40:40.590
You wanted to discuss salary?

40:40.630 --> 40:41.836
I did.

40:41.870 --> 40:43.565
I do.

40:43.600 --> 40:46.899
Well, let me gather with Will,
and see what we can do.

40:46.940 --> 40:49.932
It might not be
everything you want.

40:49.980 --> 40:52.972
I understand.

40:53.010 --> 40:55.012
(water sprinkler running)

41:17.700 --> 41:19.258
Four bedrooms, four baths,

41:19.310 --> 41:21.608
but it's definitely adaptable.

41:21.640 --> 41:23.699
This part of Highland Park

41:23.740 --> 41:26.004
is very friendly
to new construction.

41:26.050 --> 41:27.506
(continues
indistinctly)

